title: Two Dead in Quebec City Stabbing Rampage
sub_head: Police arrest mid-20s man on suspicion of killing two, injuring five others
body:
QUEBEC CITYâ€”Police in Quebec City early Sunday arrested a man on suspicion of killing two people and injuring five others in a stabbing rampage on Halloween near the provincial legislature.
Quebec police said the man, who is in his mid-20s, was taken to a hospital. In a tweet, police said their initial information indicates the motive was personal.
